      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那静止状态和移动状态之间是双向转换吗？还是只能单向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是双向的，移动后可以停下来回到静止。另外，静止状态应该是起始状态，崩溃是终态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "[*] start",
        "[*] end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来画。起始箭头指向Still，Still和Moving双向连接，Moving指向Crash作为异常终止，Still也可以直接结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "stateDiagram-v2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Crash也应该能结束吧？崩溃后这个样本的生命周期就终止了，需要加个终止箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，补上Crash到终止状态的连线。那Still也能直接结束吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，静止状态下可以直接结束样本。图名就叫\"Simple sample\"吧，简洁明了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "[*]",
        "title: Simple sample"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。检查一遍：起始到静止，静止可结束，静止和移动双向，移动可崩溃，崩溃后结束。结构清晰。",
